  <h2>Welcome to Localmart!</h2>
  <p>This page is currently in the works and will be coming soon with a variety of features to help you find local food.</p>
  <p>While we are building a wonderful experience for you to share recipes and identify local flavors and food availability we would greatly appreciate your input on what features you would like to see added.</p>
  <p><a href="/suggestions" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Suggest a Feature Â»</a></p>
